====Etymology====
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|cornet|lang=fro}}, diminutive of a popular reflex of {{etyl|la}} {{term|cornu|cornū|horn|lang=la}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/kɔɹˈnɛt/}}
* {{rhymes|ɛt}}
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈkɔːnɪt/}}
* {{rhymes|ɔː(r)nɪt}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# A [[musical instrument]] of the [[brass]] family, slightly smaller than a [[trumpet]], usually in the [[musical key]] of [[B-flat]].
# A piece of [[paper]] twisted to be used in a [[container]].
# A [[pastry]] [[shell]] to be filled with ice-cream, hence (UK) an [[ice cream cone]].

